WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:02.060
<i>Previously on "zero hour"...</i>

00:02.095 --> 00:03.344
I've seen things, dad-

00:03.380 --> 00:04.625
A nazi officer with my face.

00:04.660 --> 00:06.939
The only thing more dangerous
than hank finding out

00:06.975 --> 00:09.465
Who he really is
is someone else finding out.

00:09.500 --> 00:12.260
We're going after the cross.
The pirates will never get it.

00:12.295 --> 00:13.305
You want to know about

00:13.340 --> 00:16.140
The kid who grew up
in the orphanage.

00:16.175 --> 00:18.517
Once we find the cross,
i will tell you.

00:18.552 --> 00:20.860
Oh, my god. Theo.
I'm not going with you.

00:20.895 --> 00:22.077
This is the place
i belong now.

00:22.112 --> 00:23.926
We believed
that you were dead.

00:23.961 --> 00:25.705
The lord works
in mysterious ways.

00:25.740 --> 00:27.820
But it's not the lord's work
that you need. It's mine.

00:27.855 --> 00:29.820
This is the location
of the cross.

00:29.855 --> 00:31.300
The bugs got to it.

00:31.335 --> 00:32.785
Nobody move!

00:32.820 --> 00:34.300
It's over.
There's nothing there!

00:34.335 --> 00:36.157
Bring up the bugs.

00:36.192 --> 00:37.980
It's far from over.

00:45.840 --> 00:48.940
<i>9 is the number of judgment,</i>

00:48.975 --> 00:52.005
<i>The measure of our soul.</i>

00:52.040 --> 00:55.765
<i>When all secrets
come to light,</i>

00:55.800 --> 00:59.760
<i>The truth shall take
its toll.</i>

